track_notes: This is the easy way to summit; about 10km walk that can be a familly walk; watch the meteo before. Park the car at Bouseiyas village and enjoy

This is a nice walk to this summit. It is 2 hours drive from city of Nice...where i live. You can park at the village , free and fresh water from tape in summertime. The walk is easy, and the landscape fabulous. Plenty room on summit for antenna
